'''Ross Mullan''' is an actor based in London, England but born in Montreal, Canada.

In ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' he is playing various [[White Walkers]]. He joined the cast as a guest star in the [[Season 2|second season]] and continued in the [[Season 3|third]] and [[Season 4|fourth seasons]].
